sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Uploader
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant CJM as Cleansing Job Manager
    participant CE as Cleansing Engine
    participant JM as Validation Job Manager
    participant PF as Profiling Service
    participant RE as Rule Engine
    participant RS as Report Service
    participant MD as Metadata Registry
    participant NT as Notification Service

    U->>API: Upload dataset with cleansing enabled
    API->>CJM: Launch cleansing job
    CJM->>MD: Persist cleansing job metadata
    CJM->>CE: Execute cleansing transformations
    CE->>MD: Record cleansing metrics + output URI
    CE->>CJM: Return success with cleansed dataset reference
    CJM->>JM: Chain validation job with cleansed dataset
    JM->>PF: Request profiling snapshot (cleansed context)
    PF->>MD: Save profiling context
    PF->>RE: Provide profiling-driven context
    JM->>RE: Dispatch validation using cleansed dataset
    RE->>MD: Log rule outcomes linked to cleansing job
    RE->>RS: Send validation results
    RS->>MD: Store combined report references
    JM->>NT: Issue consolidated notification
    NT->>U: Deliver status with both job IDs
